#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/join.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.join"
msgstr "# triton.language.join"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/join.md:2
msgid "## 1 功能作用说明"
msgstr "## 1 Function Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/join.md:4
msgid "将两个相同形状的输入张量沿着新的最小维度连接，输出张量比输入张量多一个维度，大小为2，保持其他维度不变。"
msgstr "Concatenates two input tensors of the same shape along a new smallest dimension. The output tensor has one more dimension than the input tensors, with a size of 2, while keeping the other dimensions unchanged."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/join.md:6
msgid "**语法：**"
msgstr "**Syntax:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/join.md:8
msgid ""
"- `triton.language.join(x, y)` - 函数调用形式\n"
"- `x.join(y)` - 成员函数形式\n"
msgstr ""
"- `triton.language.join(x, y)` - function call form\n"
"- `x.join(y)` - member function form\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/join.md:10
msgid "**功能：**"
msgstr "**Features:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/join.md:12
msgid ""
"- 将两个相同形状的输入张量沿着新的最小维度连接\n"
"- 输出张量比输入张量多一个维度，大小为2\n"
"- 保持其他维度不变\n"
msgstr ""
"- Concatenate two input tensors of the same shape along a new minimum dimension\n"
"- The output tensor has one more dimension than the input tensors, with a size of 2\n"
"- Keep other dimensions unchanged\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/join.md:14
msgid "## 2 参数规格"
msgstr "## 2 Parameter Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/join.md:16
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/join.md:18
msgid ""
"| 参数名 | 类型 | 必需 | 说明 |\n"
"|--------|------|------|------|\n"
"| x | tensor | 是 | 第一个输入张量 |\n"
"| y | tensor | 是 | 第二个输入张量 |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type | Required | Description |\n"
"|----------------|------|----------|-------------|\n"
"| x | tensor | Yes | The first input tensor |\n"
"| y | tensor | Yes | The second input tensor |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/join.md:20
msgid "**返回值：**"
msgstr "**Return value:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/join.md:22
msgid ""
"- **类型：** tensor\n"
"- **形状：** 输入tensor广播后的形状加上一个大小为2的维度\n"
"- **数据类型：** 与输入张量相同\n"
"- **内存布局：** 在新增维度上堆叠x和y\n"
msgstr ""
"- **Type:** tensor\n"
"- **Shape:** The shape of the input tensor after broadcasting, plus a dimension of size 2\n"
"- **Data type:** Same as the input tensor\n"
"- **Memory layout:** Stack x and y along the new dimension\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/join.md:24
msgid "**约束条件：**"
msgstr "**Constraints:**"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Shape_Manipulation_Ops/join.md:26
msgid "- 两个输入张量必须具有可以广播到相同形状的形状和数据类型"
msgstr "- The two input tensors must have shapes and data types that can be broadcast to the same shape."

